{"tid":86042,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【差啲中伏】大家用app識人真係要小心","createTime":"2017-01-18T18:01:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-18T19:28:05.000Z","uid":73191,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7b62dd2a40570ed8483ebde1a1d0d6beae742f09","tid":86042,"uid":73191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T18:01:38.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n早排係某app遇到一個女仔<br />\n自稱讀緊書 <br />\n傾咗無耐個女仔就話不如轉whatsapp傾<br />\n初頭都無乜野 大家好好傾咁<br />\n去到依兩日佢開始mention美容嗰啲野<br />\n問我有無做facial又話搵日一齊去做<br />\n咁我無理佢啦 我心諗男人老狗做乜撚野facial<br />\n跟住今日佢就約我出黎見面話去食下飯做個朋友咁<br />\n問多佢兩下佢就話帶我去睇下啲facial試下<br />\n我話無興趣 之後即刻無再覆<br />\n屌 所以話（非針對）係app出現嘅女10成8 9 都係無好野 （當然唔排除有部分係真心想識人）<br />\n大家真係要小心啲！"},{"pid":"bb68c9a06b7371d3c8bc9c2053ec8807b3e4f8b8","tid":86042,"uid":76542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T18:02:57.000Z","msg":"Old new is so 唔識串"},{"pid":"18c5b9ca81bb14062e4712ff70a8027bfa6a444b","tid":86042,"uid":2300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T18:03:51.000Z","msg":"美容雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"654d3782956aba4ac01b9ff2d5916e377be3fb8a","tid":86042,"uid":3818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T18:04:11.000Z","msg":"美容雞 好多年啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b904aec7af4559b7d54e9d0431f0a5bc368b7dbb","tid":86042,"uid":2300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T18:05:01.000Z","msg":"係咪入面依幾隻<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/47251\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/47251</a>"},{"pid":"10e3fc8b5ad0d8d904587e71a8a9df42de9157aa","tid":86042,"uid":73191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T18:06:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪入面依幾隻<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/47251\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/47251</a></blockquote